payload.description: GitHub Dashboard using Ember.js and Twitter Bootstrap

issue.body:
Create rake task which deploy current version in folder `v.X.Y.Z` so the specific version can be viewed. The `gh-pages` branch therefore will then look like:

```
- index.html
- app.js
- app.css
- loader.js
- v0.0.9/
      - index.html
      - ...
- v0.0.10/
      - index.html
      - ...
```

This allows to access a specific version of the dashboard via [http://pangratz/github.com/dashboard/v0.0.9/index.html](http://pangratz/github.com/dashboard/v0.0.9/index.html) and the current version via [http://pangratz/github.com/dashboard/index.html](http://pangratz/github.com/dashboard/index.html)
